{"expireTime":9007200866810004000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-html-ast-07380752a45f5598b4289f03c404e356--","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I spent a couple weekends looking into Kubernetes, and it looks to be start of a new project. So this post will outline the plans and requirements for the different modularized microservices that I will make as part of my project, in app.simonxu.com.","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":251,"offset":251}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":251,"offset":251}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Microservice 1: Database Display","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":2,"offset":254},"end":{"line":4,"column":34,"offset":286}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":253},"end":{"line":4,"column":35,"offset":287}}},{"type":"text","value":"\nThe first one will be the most basic, it will update to show the contents of a firebase datastore including key-value pairs that are in my firebase database. This will update automatically ","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":35,"offset":287},"end":{"line":5,"column":190,"offset":477}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":253},"end":{"line":5,"column":190,"offset":477}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Microservice 2: REST API","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":2,"offset":480},"end":{"line":7,"column":26,"offset":504}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":479},"end":{"line":7,"column":27,"offset":505}}},{"type":"text","value":"\nThis will be some basic GET, POST, PUT, DELETE actions from REST base